OL,3,CMan quizzed over human trafficking
OL,4,Callegations in Al Fayed abuse
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FA man has been interviewed under
OL,8,Fcaution over allegations of human
OL,9,Ftrafficking and facilitating rape in
OL,10,Fconnection with the ongoing
OL,11,Finvestigation into former Harrods boss
OL,12,FMohamed Al Fayed.
OL,14,FThe Metropolitan Police said on Friday
OL,15,Fthe suspect, in his 60s, was
OL,16,Fquestioned this month after 154 people
OL,17,Fcame forward to report allegations of
OL,18,Fsex abuse against Al Fayed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
