OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774775625
OL,3,CMan quizzed over human trafficking
OL,4,Callegations in Al Fayed abuse
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FEarlier this month, three women were
OL,8,Falso questioned by police between
OL,9,FFebruary 25 and March 5, on suspicion
OL,10,Fof aiding and abetting rape and sexual
OL,11,Fassault, assisting the commission of
OL,12,Fsexual offences and human trafficking
OL,13,Ffor sexual exploitation.
OL,15,FNo arrests have been made and the
OL,16,Finvestigation is ongoing.
OL,18,FThe Met previously said officers had
OL,19,Ftaken accounts from Al Fayed's
OL,20,Faccusers and other witnesses over the
OL,21,Fpast 18 months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
