OL,3,CMan quizzed over human trafficking
OL,4,Callegations in Al Fayed abuse
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe force said the information from
OL,8,Fthose interviews widened the scope of
OL,9,Fthe investigation to include alleged
OL,10,Fhuman trafficking.
OL,12,FBefore any suspect was interviewed
OL,13,Funder caution, lawyers representing Al
OL,14,FFayed's alleged victims urged police
OL,15,Fto treat the scandal as "trafficking
OL,16,Fallegations".
