OL,3,CMan quizzed over human trafficking
OL,4,Callegations in Al Fayed abuse
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe Met previously announced the force
OL,8,Fis investigating individuals
OL,9,Fsurrounding Al Fayed who could have
OL,10,Fenabled him to carry out more than 400
OL,11,Fsexual misconduct crimes, which are
OL,12,Fclaimed to have spanned decades
OL,13,Fbetween 1977 and 2014.
OL,15,FAl Fayed died in 2023, aged 94.
